description: On June 24, Zohran Mamdani, a member of the Democratic Party's left wing, won the party's nomination for mayor of New York City. While his path to victory will likely be difficult, academic Mathieu Bonzom argues in his column that the rise of the American left is becoming increasingly credible.

headline: Is the postcoital moment always a sad one?
description: Studies have shed light on 'postcoital dysphoria,' which can affect women and – even more frequently – men after sexual intercourse. This condition may manifest in the form of anxiety, sadness or even irritability.
